" is a 1994 American animated epic musical film produced by Walt Disney Feature Animation and directed by Roger Allers and Rob Minkoff. It is also mentioned that the film features an ensemble voice cast that includes James Earl Jones, among other actors. Specifically, it is noted that James Earl Jones voiced the character of Mufasa in the film.', 'answer': 'Mufasa'}) (input_keys=None), Example({'augmented': True, 'context': ['Kimber Aegis | The Kimber Aegis is a series of M1911 pistols chambered in 9mm Luger and made by Kimber Manufacturing. It includes the subcompact Ultra Aegis II, the compact Pro Aegis II, and the full-sized Custom Aegis II.', 'Malinnov pistol | The Malinnov M1P is an improved NATO-standard 9×19 mm Parabellum round, a series of polymer-framed, short recoil-operated, double-action semi-automatic pistols designed and produced since 2015 by Aegis Malinnov Sdn Bhd, located in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia and will be launched before the Langkawi International Maritime and Aerospace Exhibition (LIMA) 2015. Malinnov also offer 1911-style pistols using double-stacked magazines with significantly larger capacities (typically 16 rounds).', 'Kimber Manufacturing | Kimber Manufacturing is an American company that designs, manufactures, and distributes small arms such as M1911 pistols, Solo pistols and rifles. The USA Shooting Team, Marines assigned to Special Operations Command, and the LAPD SWAT team use Kimber pistols.', 'Kimber Custom | The Kimber Custom is an M1911 style semi-automatic pistol. It is designed, manufactured, and distributed by Kimber Manufacturing, Inc. in Yonkers, New York.'], 'question': 'Kimber Aegis is a series of which single-action pistols?', 'reasoning': 'The context provided mentions that the Kimber Aegis is a series of M1911 pistols. M1911 pistols are single-action pistols, as stated in the description of the Kimber Aegis.', 'answer': 'M1911'}) (input_keys=None)]

